		<title>Dudi Ben Simon’s Playful Photos Draw on Visual Puns and Humourous Happenstance</title>
		<link>https://www.sawberries.com/2024/04/29/dudi-ben-simon-photos/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ross]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 15:30:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[art]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Dudi Ben Simon]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[humor]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Photography]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.sawberries.com/2024/04/29/dudi-ben-simon-photos/</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[All images © Dudi Ben Simon, shared with permission When Dudi Ben Simon observes the world around her, visual puns and parallels are everywhere: a cinnamon bun stands in for a hair bun; the crinkled top of a lemon is cinched like a handbag; or yellow rubber glove stretches like melted cheese. “I see it as [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>
<div id="attachment_246152" style="width: 1546px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246152" class="wp-image-246152 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-6.jpg" alt="two pieces of toast pulling a yellow rubber glove that looks like the cheese in a grilled cheese sandwich" width="1536" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-6.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-6-640x800.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-6-960x1200.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-6-1229x1536.jpg 1229w" sizes="(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246152" class="wp-caption-text">All images © Dudi Ben Simon, shared with permission</p>
</div>
<p>When <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dudibensimon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dudi Ben Simon</a> observes the world around her, visual puns and parallels are everywhere: a cinnamon bun stands in for a hair bun; the crinkled top of a lemon is cinched like a handbag; or yellow rubber glove stretches like melted cheese. “I see it as a type of readymade, a trend in art created by using objects or daily life items disconnected to their original context, changing their meanings and creating a new story from them,” the artist says. “I attempt to preserve the regular appearance of the items, but with a switch.”</p>
<p>Ben Simon also takes inspiration from the directness of advertising, focusing on a finely tuned, deceptively simple message that can both be read quickly and provoke humor or curiosity. “I truly believe in minimalism,” she says. “What is not required to tell the story does not exist.”</p>
<p>See more playful takes on everyday objects on Ben Simon’s <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dudibensimon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>. You might also enjoy <a href="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/2023/10/eric-kogan-new-york-photos/">Eric Kogan</a>’s serendiptous street photography around New York City.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246153 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-5.jpg" alt="a croissant with dark brown stripes with a belt buckle extending from it as if the belt has been wrapped around the pastry" width="1433" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-5.jpg 1433w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-5-640x858.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-5-960x1286.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-5-1146x1536.jpg 1146w" sizes="(max-width: 1433px) 100vw, 1433px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246156 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2up.jpg" alt="two image side by side showing, on the left, a wine bottle positioned like the heel of a stiletto with a cork next to it, and on the right, a lemon with the crinkled top around the stem looking cinched by an attached purse string" width="1920" height="1264" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2up.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2up-640x421.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2up-960x632.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2up-1536x1011.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246158 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-1.jpg" alt="a photograph of a woman with her hair tied up in a bun, and a cinnamon bun situated where her own hair bun would be" width="1440" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-1.jpg 1440w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-1-640x853.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-1-960x1280.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-1-1152x1536.jpg 1152w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246154 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-4.jpg" alt="a yellow Birkenstock sandal with a banana peel strapped through one of the buckles" width="1433" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-4.jpg 1433w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-4-640x858.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-4-960x1286.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-4-1146x1536.jpg 1146w" sizes="(max-width: 1433px) 100vw, 1433px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246155 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-3.jpg" alt="a yellow rubber glove drapes off of a shelf, with a broken egg shell near it, resembling the liquid part of the egg dripping" width="1427" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-3.jpg 1427w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-3-640x861.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-3-960x1292.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-3-1142x1536.jpg 1142w" sizes="(max-width: 1427px) 100vw, 1427px"> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246157 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2.jpg" alt="a daisy with a missing petal, which is replaced by a woman's long, white fingernail that resembles the shape of a petal" width="1350" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2.jpg 1350w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2-640x910.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2-960x1365.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dudi-2-1080x1536.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px"></p>
